{"title":"官厅小集","authors":["吕剑"],"dates":[{"year":1956,"month":11,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"官厅小集"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吕剑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看山头的烽火台上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还照着秦代的斜阳；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但在工人的欢呼声中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"升起了一道拦河长城。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拦河坝确是真正的长城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它叫永定河真正的永定；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就在这一带荒山平原间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将见湖光闪耀山色青青。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚云低笼着远山和近谷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明月还没有从东方上升；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深山里忽见灯火闪闪万点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听少女歌唱声声恍如仙境。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不仅官厅电站让我们惊讶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它只是我们的第一朵鲜花；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全国到处都将辉耀着电光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请看那三门峡刘家峡巫峡……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1955年—1956年"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}